<p>Dave&#39;s back from WWDC and he and John focus on your questions this week. How best can one enable Airplane Mode on a Mac? How do you find a missing Mailbox? Why does the iTunes Library stay put when you tell it to move? And&#8230; what happened with John&#39;s phone? Was it the charger? Was it the app? We have answers!</p>
